oads/2020/05/18May_StreetTraders_DW-8-270x180.jpg 270w, https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/18May_StreetTraders_DW-8-560x373.jpg 560w" sizes="(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px" />8 May 2020: Mercy Mokgehle and Zandile Mbatha choose spring onions for their vegetable stalls at the Yeoville Market.



